FAQs

frequently asked questions

Can You Integrate My Existing Software With New Applications Or Systems?

Yes, we offer ERP/CRM integrations services that ensure seamless integration of your existing software with new applications or systems. This allows for better data synchronization and improved operational efficiency.

How Do You Ensure The Security Of My Software Project?

Security is one of our top priorities. We incorporate secure coding practices and conduct regular vulnerability assessments and code reviews to ensure your software is secure from potential threats.

How do you manage communication with different time zones?

At Hashlogics, we use flexible scheduling, dedicated project managers, and asynchronous communication tools to ensure seamless and effective communication across all time zones.

Would you have rights to my product after the development is finished?

All work produced by Hashlogics will become the sole intellectual property of your company. Hashlogics reserves the right to use visual representations of the final product as part of our project portfolio. We will not disclose any confidential information regarding the project and will be responsible for the code as well.

How do you handle project timelines and what project management tools do you use?

We employ agile project management methodologies to ensure timely delivery. Our approach involves setting clear milestones and keeping you updated throughout the project to ensure we meet deadlines effectively. For efficient project management, we utilize a range of tools including Asana, ClickUp, Jira, Airtable, Trello, Slack, Notion, and more.

Do you offer post-launch support and maintenance?

Yes! We offer comprehensive ongoing support for the CMS following development. We provide complimentary maintenance for one month to address any bugs or functionality issues that arise within the platform we developed. Please note that the addition of new functionalities or modules is not included in this maintenance period.

What is your pricing model?

Our pricing model varies depending on the scope and complexity of the project. We offer competitive rates and can provide a detailed estimate after understanding your project requirements.

How do I get started with a project at Hashlogics?

You can get started by contacting us through our website or directly emailing us. We’ll schedule a consultation to discuss your project requirements and how we can help.
